Winter skincare routine ✨🌼 with @jaivique 

Let’s learn about the brand first 
✅Their products are vegan,dermatologically tested as safe ,highly effective and non-comedogenic. 
✅The products are free from parabens, SLS, Mineral oil , Artificial colours, silicones ,propylene glycol and Formaldehyde. 
✅70% of the water waste is treated and recycled. 

✨Now coming to the products ✨
@jaivique  was kind enough to send me their sheer skin body lotion , sun safe spf and hydrating face gel (this one is my favourite)😍

💫Hydrating Face Gel contains sea buckthorn extract , Hyaluronic acid and Vitamin C. It is a light gel that easily absorbs into the skin leaving it hydrated and plump without making it sticky. I personally love the glow it gives💕

💫Sun safe spf 45 contains raspberries ,carrot extract and shea butter. The consistency is thick but settles completely matte. Takes time to blend but causes no pilling. Works perfectly under the makeup too. 

💫Sheer skin body lotion contains hemp oil, avocado oil and sea buckthorn extract. The consistency isn’t runny once settled it provides hydration for more than 5-6hours (I have extremely dry skin type). The fragrance isn’t overpowering and doesn’t stay for long. 

Thankyouu so much @jaivique for sending these products. I am extremely grateful for the opportunity ✨

If there is one thing I can’t get over it is their Hydrating Face gel. I would highly suggest you to try it out once. 

**products are kindly sent by the brand but all the opinions are my own.
